high_descs: Make a left, then another left around the kitchen island to reach the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn to face the tomato in the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink with the knife.
Turn to face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Set the knife down on the countertop.
Turn left to face the sink.
Pick up a slice of the tomato in the sink.
Turn right to walk towards the microwave.
Heat up the slice of tomato in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk to the fridge across the room.
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato to heat up in the microwave and place in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward and to the left to the sink.
Take the knife from the sink.
Stay at the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Turn to the right.
Put the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn left to the sink.
Take a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right, go forward to the oven.
Cook the slice of tomato in the microwave above the oven. Take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, walk straight, turn left, turn right to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn left from the sink.
Turn left, turn left to the green counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn left to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right, turn right, Walk straight to the oven.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, turn on the microwave. Close the door. Open the microwave.
Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato at the top.
anns.task_desc: Put a sliced tomato into a fridge.
